title: Counts of Balsam-fir Seedlings
description:
Description
The fir data frame has 50 rows and 3 columns.
The number of balsam-fir seedlings in each quadrant of a grid of 50 five foot 
square quadrants were counted.  The grid consisted of 5 rows of 10 quadrants in
each row.
reference:
Davison, A.C. and Hinkley, D.V. (1997) 
Bootstrap Methods and Their Application. Cambridge University Press.

parameters.count: The number of seedlings in the quadrant.
parameters.row: The row number of the quadrant.
parameters.col: The quadrant number within the row.
